### ======================================================
### STAGEFLOW - SUBSCRIPTION CHECKOUT (CONTRATO)
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@checkoutId = REPLACE_CHECKOUT_ID
@ownerToken = REPLACE_OWNER_TOKEN
@subscriberToken = REPLACE_SUBSCRIBER_TOKEN

### @name startCheckout
### ✅ Iniciar checkout (plano + dados + domínio + pagamento)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "PROFESSIONAL",
  "billingCycle": "ANNUAL",
  "studioName": "Rock Valley Studio",
  "ownerName": "Carlos Mendes",
  "ownerEmail": "contato@rockvalley.com.br",
  "ownerPhone": "(11) 99999-9999",
  "ownerDocument": "000.000.000-00",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "rockvalley-{{$timestamp}}",
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "totalAmount": 1970
}

### ✅ Consultar status de checkout
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}

### ✅ Aprovar checkout (V1 manual por OWNER)
### @name approveCheckout
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentReference": "evt_payment_ok_123"
}

### ✅ Adicionar sala via Settings (assinante USER vinculado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/studios/{{approveCheckout.response.body.checkout.studioId}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sala A - Ensaio",
  "type": "rehearsal",
  "description": "Ideal para bandas e ensaios.",
  "pricePerHour": 80,
  "capacity": 6,
  "features": ["Bateria acústica", "PA 1000W"]
}

### ❌ Approve sem token OWNER (deve retornar 401/403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentReference": "evt_payment_without_owner"
}

### ❌ Subdomínio indisponível (deve retornar 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "STARTER",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "studioName": "Outro Studio",
  "ownerName": "Ana",
  "ownerEmail": "ana@studio.com",
  "ownerPhone": "(11) 90000-0000",
  "ownerDocument": "111.111.111-11",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "rockvalley",
  "paymentMethod": "PIX",
  "totalAmount": 80
}
